[6] Pakistan: (Lahore)
Date: Thu 25 Oct 2007
Source: The News International [edited]
<http://www.thenews.com.pk/daily_detail.asp?id=77043>


The total number of recorded dengue fever cases has risen to 11 in Punjab,
including 8 in Lahore alone, said reports [arriving at the] provincial
Directorate General of Health Services.

In Sir Ganga Ram Hospital on Wednesday [24 Oct 2007], 3 fresh patients have
been confirmed dengue fever positive here besides 5 dengue fever cases
detected in the provincial metropolis before yesterday [24 Oct 2007].

